title: 이달의소녀탐구 #193 (LOONA TV #193)
members: Choerry, Kim Lip, JinSoul, YeoJin, HaSeul
summary:
0:04 -- PD asks JinSoul whether she is tired and JinSoul replies that she is fine. Choerry
adds that she isn’t tired.
0:14 -- Lippie explains that Choerry said that Soul should be tired because she is 4 years
older. Soul: “Choerry really has pride of her age.”
0:26 -- The three share a room with YeoJin and it is just YeoJin alone right now so they
wrote her a letter. Then they start being mean to her (in a friendly way ofc)
0:45 -- Cut to YeoSeul who are having fun.
